<p>On this page you will find regular updates and briefings provided by the Trafford CCG PHB Team.</p>
<h4>Law Change to Provide Thousands More With Access to Personal Health Budgets</h4>
<p>For more information on the change visit the&nbsp;Association of Mental Health Providers <a class="sys_16" href="https://amhp.org.uk/law-change-to-provide-thousands-more-with-access-to-personal-health-budgets/">website</a>.</p>
<h4>This is your time to shine -&nbsp;Enter the Accolades 2020</h4>
<p>Do you work with individual employers who are committed to developing their own and their personal assistant&rsquo;s (PAs) skills? <a class="sys_16" href="https://www.skillsforcare.org.uk/Getting-involved/accolades/Accolades.aspx?utm_source=email&amp;utm_medium=skillsforcare&amp;utm_term=accolades-ULO-email&amp;utm_content=accolades-ULO-email&amp;utm_campaign=Accolades2020">Nominate them</a> for an Accolades award so that they get recognised for the great work they do.&nbsp;<a class="sys_16" href="https://www.skillsforcare.org.uk/Getting-involved/accolades/Accolades.aspx">Accolades 2020</a></p>
<h4>Personal Health Budgets to beome the default delivery model for NHS Continuing Healthcare Funded Home Care by April 2019</h4>
<p>For full details <a title="PHBs Default Offer" class="sys_21" href="/docs/About-us/Personal-Health-Budgets/PHBs-Default-Offer.pdf">please click here.</a></p>
<h4>Learning and development opportunities</h4>
<p><a target="_blank" class="sys_16" href="https://www.skillsforcare.org.uk/Learning-development/Care-Certificate/Care-Certificate.aspx">Please click here</a> for details of &lsquo;The Care Certificate&rsquo; an agreed set of standards that set out the knowledge, skills and behaviours expected of specific job roles in the health and social care sectors.</p>
